data.description: $10K PRICE REDUCTION and immediate equity!!  Motivated Sellers VA ASSUMEABLE at 2.5% interest rate for VA Eligible Buyers!!  NO DOWN PAYMENT with 100% USDA financing!!  Will provide some closing cost with full price offer.  This beautiful home centrally located in Aiken County features 3 bedrooms 2.5 half baths. The beautiful kitchen features a breakfast area, granite countertops, tile back splash, and pantry.  The owner suite features a spacious closet with ensuite bath with separate shower and tub with double vanity sink.  The other bedrooms are spacious with walk-in closets. Close to I-20, schools, medical, SRS, Fort Gordon and downtown Augusta and Aiken.
